  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8, \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u00a0 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Protests are taking place in Kotakalai and Thalawakalai demanding the resignation of the President",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Protests were also carried out in Thalawakalai and Kotakalai today demanding the resignation of President Gotabaya Rajapaksa.",
        "Shops were closed in the said cities and traders also extended their support to the people's protest.",
        "Civil society activists, youth, tricycle drivers joined the protest.",
        "Also, a branch of Kota Ko Gama also sprung up in Thalawakkala town. The Kota Ko Kama branch has been formed to continue the protest until the President and the government headed by him resign.",
        "Many people living in Thalawakalai and its surrounding areas participated in the protest and supported the ongoing protest in Colombo.",
        "Meanwhile, in Kotakalai city, city traders, civil society activists, youth, teachers and children participated in the protest."
      ],
